    ("Sexual selection in marine species can produce:", ["identical appearances in males and females", "elaborate male features like the narwhal tusk or humpback whale song", "loss of all secondary sexual characteristics", "only camouflage coloration"], 1, "Mate choice drives evolution of conspicuous traits."),
