    ("Marine reserves (no-take zones) benefit fisheries by:", ["removing all fish from the area", "providing refuge for fish to grow and reproduce, eventually spilling over into fished areas", "reducing overall fish stocks", "only protecting coral reefs"], 1, "Spillover and larval export benefit adjacent fisheries."),
