    ("The Galápagos Marine Reserve demonstrates that:", ["MPAs hurt tourism", "large MPAs can protect unique biodiversity while supporting sustainable tourism", "no species benefit from protection", "only terrestrial species need protection"], 1, "Marine tourism generates significant revenue."),
